Malyari ka muring manintun text kareng articulu. Munta ka mu king "search" field king kayli, isulat me ing search term, at i-click me ing "search". Malyari ya palang tuknang ing search function sakaling mika-server overload; nung milyari ita, ituru ra kang king metung a [[Google]]-based a search ning Wikipedia database. Atin muring [[Wikipedia:Searching|aliwang paralan]] ban [[Wikipedia:Readers%27_FAQ#How_do_I_search_Wikipedia.3F|manintun king Wikipedia]].

Nung atin kang abasang talagang aburi mu, malyari mung sabyan king [[Wikipedia:talk page|talk page]] ning articulu. Mumuna, pilan me ing '''discussion''' link (paintunan me karetang tab king babo ning page), ba kang miras king talk page. Kaybat, pilinan me ing '''edit this page''' ketang talk page, o i-click me ing '''+''' king wanan ning '''edit this page''' bang mamyeng bayung comentu. Maka-cusuelu kekami ing ditak a puri.

Nu namang ating paksang ala pa keti, o e magkasakit kang manintun ketang kekang paksa, mangutang ka mu ketang [[Wikipedia:reference desk|reference desk]], o idagdag me itang paksang ketang [[Wikipedia:requested articles|requested articles]]. Lumawe kang aliwang paralan bang [[Wikipedia:Explore|lumibut king Wikipedia]] o... [[Help:Starting a new page|sumulat king sarili mung articulu]].

== Pamag-edit ==
Angyang ninu, makapag-edit page king Wikipedia — angga ing page a ini! I-click me mu ing '''edit this page''' a link king babo ning sanumang page (except for [[Wikipedia:This page is protected|protected pages]]) nung king palage mu mangaylangan yang samasan o dagdagan informacion. Ala kang kaylangang nanumang e mu sadyang gagamitan; angyang ping e ka [[Wikipedia:How to log in|maka-log in]]. Nung bisa ka pang mag-experimentu, itang e ka makasira king tutung articulu, munta ka king [[Wikipedia:Sandbox|the sandbox]], nung nu ka makapag-practis anggang buri mu. Nu namang buri meng pag-practisan itang sadya nang page a anti kanini, copian me mu at i-paste manibat king edit page ning articulu papunta king sandbox. Nu namang buri mung miragdagan ing balu mu, lon me ing [[Wikipedia:Tutorial|Wikipedia Tutorial]] ba mung abalu ing peka-simpling kaylangan mung abalu anting kayanib king kekatamung proyectu. 

Malyaring makabaligo ngan ini kabang purmeru pero lon me ing, [[Wikipedia:Replies to common objections|pakibat kareng karaniwan a reclamu]] nu nukarin maki pamipalino nung bakit gagana ya pa murin ing sistemang iti.

== Policies ==
Atin tamung mapilan a [[Wikipedia:policies and guidelines|policies and guidelines]] a kaylangan mung lon. Deng atlung peka-maulaga ila pin ding NPOV, GFDL, ampong civility. What does this mean?
* Ing NPOV, o [[Wikipedia:neutral point of view|neutral point of view]] buri nang sabyan ala lang papanigan deng articulu, at patas ing pamagprisinta na kareng miyayaliwang pamalak king metung a paksa.
* Mililimbag la reng anggang articulung ambag king Wikipedia king lalam ning [[GNU Free Documentation License]] (GFDL). Sisiguradua'na niting timawa ing pangalimbag ning Wikipedia kabang panaun. Pakisabi ming mayap a e ko manambag articulu o nanumang bageng maki copyright nung alang paintulut ketang tatalan king copyright. (Lawan me ing [[Wikipedia:Copyrights|Copyrights]] para king karagdagang informacion).
* Civility. Ing palakad king Wiki magdependi king pamisaup-saup, anya dapat miral ing respetu king metung at metung, [[Wikipedia:Civility|pamangalang]], ampong [[Wikipedia:Wikilove|lugud a wiki]] . Sana [[Wikipedia:Assume good faith|dinan mong pamikatagun deng aliwa]] neng ating e pamikaintindi, [[Wikipedia:Staying cool when the editing gets hot|manatili kang calmadu]], at misabi kong masalese. Metung yang masanting a akasanayan ing mamye [[Wikipedia:edit summary|edit summary]] nung nu mo isplican deng inalilan mu, ba rong apansinan at tanggapan deng aliwa detang kekang gewa. Nung akit mung milako la o miyalilan detang kekang in-edit, manaya ka saguli bayu mo ibalik. Lon me pamu ing page history, ing kekang talk page, itang talk page ning articulu. Lawan me murin ing [[Wikipedia:Wikiquette|Wikiquette]].

== E ka masisira lub ==
Nung danasan mu ing e-pamikasundu potang magumpisa kang mag-edit, e ka milalako gana. E mu alako ing miyayaliwa pamalak king sanu mang proyectung daka'la reng sasaup. Basan me ing [[Wikipedia:Writers rules of engagement|writers' rules of engagement]] page ampo reng miyayaliwang articulo king dake ning pamanuru (tutorial wing) king lalam. Gamitan mu king pamaglutas da reng kekang prublema ba kang mabyasang maging kayanib a actibu at dakal agagawa. 

At nung atin kang e aintindian, — technical man o tungkul king pamakyabe, — at e ka siguradu nung nu ka lumawe, magpaskil ka mung kutang king [[Wikipedia:help desk]], at manakit kang macusuelung sumaup keka.

Have fun!

